org.eclipse.scada.configuration.world.osgi

Interface EquinoxApplication

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Application, Documentable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ArduinoDriver, CustomMasterServer, DefaultMasterServer, DefaultValueArchiveServer, MasterServer, ModbusDriver, ValueArchiveServer
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ArduinoDriverImpl, CustomMasterServerImpl, DefaultMasterServerImpl, DefaultValueArchiveServerImpl, MasterServerImpl, ModbusDriverImpl, ValueArchiveServerImpl

    public interface EquinoxApplication
extends Application
    A representation of the model object 'Equinox Application'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Connections
    • Exporter
    • Customization Profile
    • Security Configuration
    • Modules

    See Also:
    OsgiPackage.getEquinoxApplication()
